2) Your Lego / Pokémon insight — this is the same mechanism

What you described is value = story × structure × scarcity

Not material.

⸻

Same plastic, different geometry of exchange
	•	Material layer → identical (plastic bricks)
	•	Story layer → different (Darth Vader vs generic set)
	•	Market layer → different buyers, different willingness to pay
	•	Scarcity layer → controlled supply → perceived rarity

So the “fight” isn’t:

plastic vs plastic

It’s:

meaning vs meaning in a constrained supply space

